Class Summary
ImageMotionPointKey<I extends ImageSingleBand,T extends InvertibleTransform> Computes the transform from the first image in a sequence to the current frame.
MotionMosaicPointKey<I extends ImageSingleBand,T extends InvertibleTransform> Extension of ImageMotionPointKey specifically designed for creating image mosaics.
MotionStabilizePointKey<I extends ImageSingleBand,T extends InvertibleTransform> Extension of ImageMotionPointKey specifically designed to stabilize image motion.
PruneCloseTracks Detects if tracks are too close together and discards some of the close ones.
RenderImageMotion<I extends ImageSingleBand,O extends ImageBase> Creates a mosaic by batching together smaller images with their respective transforms.
